  "2117430": {
    "name": "Purrrifiers: Cleaning Chaos",
    "steam_appid": 2117430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Purrrifiers: Cleaning Chaos</u></strong> 融合了混乱、荒诞幽默和真实的合作玩法，定义了其独特的怪诞类型——“Goofylike”。这是一场混乱、魔法与猫咪齐聚的冒险，团队合作、创造力以及一丝疯狂是生存（和清理）所必需的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧹<strong>清理、施法与制造混乱</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/ce4cfaa7c7e6327f528e58c7a8b5a863.poster.avif?t=1772203617\" width=800 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/ce4cfaa7c7e6327f528e58c7a8b5a863.webm?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/ce4cfaa7c7e6327f528e58c7a8b5a863.mp4?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一半是清洁模拟器，一半是狂热梦境，《Purrrifiers: Cleaning Chaos》将玩家投放到一个拖把与魔法相遇，每个混乱背后都隐藏故事的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索<strong>警察局</strong>、<strong>主播之家</strong>、<strong>巫师的家</strong>、<strong>地下隧道</strong>、<strong>燃烧的龙之战场</strong>，甚至还有一个<strong>由非常有礼貌的鹿统治的森林</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务？<strong>让它闪闪发光</strong>——或者至少不要那么恶心。在旅途中，你将面对<strong>Toiletmort</strong>，<strong>清理电脑中的数字诅咒</strong>，<strong>洗衣服</strong>，并<strong>抚摸数量不合理的猫</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧽<strong>疯狂工具</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/929d0ab7efc30d5deb89ac49566c3193.poster.avif?t=1772203617\" width=800 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/929d0ab7efc30d5deb89ac49566c3193.webm?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/929d0ab7efc30d5deb89ac49566c3193.mp4?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以在各种荒诞而令人满意的清洁工具之间切换，包括：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高压清洗机、吸尘器、海绵、喷雾以及魔法棒</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >彩色垃圾桶（为仍然相信秩序的人准备）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >绳索上的吸盘、收集薯片用的薯片袋，以及传奇的<strong>Poop Stick™</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作与熔化工作台，用于升级你的清洁帝国</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>垃圾场沙盒</strong>中，玩家可以清洗程序生成的垃圾，获取资源，并建造终极回收要塞。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧼<strong>不仅仅是肥皂和水</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/d4811539c7cd98bde11a62625269b93a.poster.avif?t=1772203617\" width=800 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/d4811539c7cd98bde11a62625269b93a.webm?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/d4811539c7cd98bde11a62625269b93a.mp4?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开放世界</strong>，充满剧情任务、秘密和垃圾</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>会说话的猫</strong>，提供任务（偶尔也会给人生建议）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>增益和减益</strong>，如尴尬伤害、电击和治疗之吻</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>魔法与混乱相遇</strong>——用魔杖清洁、击败Boss、解决奇怪的谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>合作或单人游戏</strong>——团队合作让梦想般的清洁成为可能</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐈<strong>关于清洁（和猫）的混乱合作喜剧</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/867a155cf5d392e71f2b7e0c6091b604.poster.avif?t=1772203617\" width=800 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/867a155cf5d392e71f2b7e0c6091b604.webm?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2117430/extras/867a155cf5d392e71f2b7e0c6091b604.mp4?t=1772203617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Purrrifiers: Cleaning Chaos》并不追求完美——它强调<strong>拥抱混乱、在杂乱中欢笑，并庆祝每一个半干净的角落</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它是<strong>Goofylike</strong>，荒诞不经，并在等待着你。抓住一个朋友，抚摸一只猫，准备好你的魔杖。因为在这个世界里，清洁可能接近“猫咪感”，但混乱永远不会远离。</p>",
